src:
Bilweb i nytt annonssamarbete med Bonnier News
Nu blir Bilweb bättre för både bilköpare och bilsäljare! Genom ett nytt samarbete med Sveriges ledande mediabolag Bonnier News ska Bilwebs kunder nå nya målgrupper i hela Sverige.
07 Nov 2019, 08:00 by Bonnier News MID

text:
Car web in new advertising collaboration with Bonnier News
Now Bilweb is getting better for both car buyers and car sellers! Through a new collaboration with Sweden's leading media company Bonnier News, Bilweb's customers will reach new target groups throughout Sweden.
07 Nov 2019, 08:00 at Bonnier News MID
